appetizer or not? [scoffs]

566
00:26:03,515 --> 00:26:05,308
Yeah, well, we're already
getting my mom's discount.

567
00:26:05,392 --> 00:26:08,811
Yeah, well, I'm pretty
sure free is cheaper than 40%...

568
00:26:08,895 --> 00:26:10,730
- but I'm no mathmagician.
- [chuckles]

569
00:26:11,689 --> 00:26:13,107
Hey, isn't that Kenny and Abby?

570
00:26:13,190 --> 00:26:15,192
Oh, yeah, it is.

571
00:26:15,277 --> 00:26:16,319
- Hey, guys.
- Hi.

572
00:26:16,403 --> 00:26:18,154
Hey, Colt. Hi, Heather.

573
00:26:19,113 --> 00:26:21,198
Uh, oh, Kenny, your, uh,
napkin fell on your lap.

574
00:26:23,951 --> 00:26:25,712
- So, how are you guys doing?
- [Kenny] Good.

575
00:26:25,745 --> 00:26:27,497
Just celebrating our anniversary.

576
00:26:27,580 --> 00:26:29,499
We had our first date
here five years ago.

577
00:26:29,582 --> 00:26:31,584
Yeah, anyway, nice to see you two.

578
00:26:31,668 --> 00:26:32,917
I'm sure you wanna get going

579
00:26:32,942 --> 00:26:34,903
and enjoy a nice
dinner at your own table.

580
00:26:34,962 --> 00:26:36,548
Easy, Ken Dog.

581
00:26:36,631 --> 00:26:38,425
I'm pretty sure this barrel's
big enough for the both of us.

582
00:26:38,508 --> 00:26:39,592
[chuckles]

583
00:26:39,676 --> 00:26:41,761
No, I'm sorry. I just meant
that it would be better if...

584
00:26:41,844 --> 00:26:43,805
Oh, look at that. You
got the chocolate...

585
00:26:43,888 --> 00:26:45,139
Fuck me.

586
00:26:48,476 --> 00:26:51,354
Kenny, is that... Are you...

587
00:26:51,438 --> 00:26:52,855
Sweetie... [sighs]

588
00:26:52,939 --> 00:26:55,567
Uh, this isn't how I
planned it, but, uh...

589
00:26:58,277 --> 00:27:02,699
Ah... [stammers] you are
smart, you're beautiful...

590
00:27:02,782 --> 00:27:04,951
you're oddly competitive.

591
00:27:05,034 --> 00:27:06,328
[chuckles]

592
00:27:06,411 --> 00:27:07,442
You could have picked

593
00:27:07,467 --> 00:27:09,480
anybody in the world, and you chose me.

594
00:27:12,417 --> 00:27:14,920
I love you more than
anything in the world.

595
00:27:15,002 --> 00:27:16,629
- [chuckles]
- Abby Phillips...

596
00:27:18,340 --> 00:27:21,217
- [smacks lips] will you marry me?
- [gasps]

597
00:27:21,300 --> 00:27:23,803
Yes. Of course.

598
00:27:23,886 --> 00:27:25,054
[gasps]

599
00:27:27,765 --> 00:27:28,975
